Feed handler
============
Incorporate RSS and Atom feeds as MH messages.

Install::

    pip3 install fh

View help::

    $ fh -help
    SYNOPSIS
      fh [-help] [options] 
    INPUTS
      (None)
    OPTIONS
      folder: Root MH Folder to store feeds in
      feedsfile: File with feeds, with one feed per row, each row containing the
                 feed identifier, a colon, then the URL. This format is a subset of
                 mh-alias foramt. The URL may include "${page}", which will be
                 substituted for page numbers to download multiple pages.
      rcvstore: rcvstore executable
